headline: Risk-On As U.S.-China Take Step Away From Brink, Market Shrugs Off New U.S. Levy On Canada, And Milei Does Better Than Expected In Argentina
summary: The greenback (DXY) is mostly softer, and the other G10 currencies are up less than 0.2%. The PBOC set the dollar's reference rate at a new low since the middle of October 2024.
